Title: The Parking Garage
Plot: Everyone separates to try to find the car in a huge parking garage. Jerry needs to use the bathroom so he finds a place to go and gets busted. Elaine tries to get help from people passing by. George joins Jerry in getting busted. Kramer is wearing "the jacket," and forgets where he put down the air conditioner he was carrying and causes George to be really late for his parent's 47th anniversary.
GuestStars: Larry David, David Dunard, Cynthia Ettinger, Gregory Daniel, Carlyle King, Adam Wylie, Joe Farago, Ron Evans, Tucker Smallwood
